6. Testing

The following tests were successfully completed:

Uploaded employees.json to Amazon S3.
Verified S3 triggered the Lambda function.
Confirmed employee records were inserted into DynamoDB.
Accessed the API Gateway endpoint and received JSON data.
Verified the EC2-hosted website displayed employee records successfully.
