8. Conclusion

This project successfully implements an event-driven cloud architecture using AWS services. The system automatically processes uploaded employee data and displays the processed information through a web application hosted on Amazon EC2. The solution demonstrates the integration of S3, Lambda, DynamoDB, API Gateway, and EC2 to build a scalable and serverless data processing workflow.
